{\b #{\footnote html_intro.htm_techinfo}Technical Information}\sa240\par\pard\plain
ModPlug Tracker is a 32-bit Win32 application, featuring a lot of 
options to create the best possible output (Up to 48KHz, 16-bit, stereo):\line
- 32-bit internal precision for mixing, dithered to 16-bit.\line
- Very high quality resampling filter.\line
- Support for MMX/3DNow!/SSE instructions\line
- Automatic click removal\line
- Digital Bass Expansion filter (filter range and depth customizable in Advanced Player Options)\line
- Dolby Pro-Logic Surround support with custom delay.\line
- Reverberator engine, with environment presets. 
- HF Noise Reduction: attenuation of the background noise by filtering very high 
  frequencies in the sound.\line
- Stereo Separation option (25%-400%), useful for headphones.\line
- 6-bands Graphic Equalizer (requires fast floating point support).\line
- DirectSound support for low-latency mixing on hardware-accelerated soundcards\line
\line
\sa240\par\pard\plain
